{
  "stem": "4226.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they didn't-- weren't specific.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just you had to give them any valuables.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And- and-",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They- Money and valuables.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you could take small carriage-- what you can carry with you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were taken to the synagogue next door to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all Jewish families from other villages were there for about two days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we were taken by drawn horse carriages to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to the Somlyo-- Szilagy-Somlyo that, that town 18 kilometers away, which they had a disused brick factory, which had a railway line come to it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Hungarian name?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Szilagy-Somlyo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "S-Z-I-L-A-G-Y dash Somlyo, S-O-M-L-Y-O.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To that, that's-- actually, they were gendarmes--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--from the village.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I only took some food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some clothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- we were heading for spring.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was spring, practically, already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't take too many things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I, I remember one thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- I had a-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] What I took, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what I didn't take, I remember more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took my watch, a Certina chrome Swiss watch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I hid my bike.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a, a bike, a German Miele.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They produced bikes those days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now they produce [LAUGHS] dishwashers, mainly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I even cut the tires.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The tires of your bike.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she-- they confiscated the jewelry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to give what she had on her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think she took with her-- they were-- they were actually waiting for you to pack and go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They stood over you while--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They stood over you, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a matter of half an hour, and off you-- off you go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You signed some--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Into the synagogue, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And people from other villages.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
